highlights.text: “Fire On Fire - From "Watership Down"” by Sam Smith is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 83 spots at #91.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 105 weeks straight.
“Crushed Up” by Future is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #79.
XXXTENTACION has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Arms Around You (feat. Maluma & Swae Lee)” is the highest at #20.
